; The BSON value type — the canonical in-memory value shared by the query engine, Minimongo,
; and (later) the native driver. Deliberately dependency-free (Stdlib only — no Eio/Unix/Yojson)
; so the SAME source compiles to native OCaml and, via js_of_ocaml, to JavaScript for the npm
; bundle. Inline tests live in ../test (this library stays dep-free so it cross-compiles cleanly).

(library
 (name bson)
 (public_name fennec-mongo.bson))
